sources.title: Irish McCalla is Sheena: Queen of the Jungle (1955) Pulp TV Serial: Directed by Carl K. Hittleman
sources.description:
Leaping from comic panels to live-action glory! With only a knife and her animal allies, she protects the Jungle from poachers, colonizers, and treasure hunters. No CGI, no wires... just pure 1950s pulp power!

Original Title: Queen of the Jungle (1935)
